CREATED:20230914T181058Z
DESCRIPTION:Kaylin R. Boyd is a fantasy author. She was born in the Midwest
 \, and raised on a strict diet of daydreams\, myth\, and magic. She has pub
 lished an illustrated book of prose\, The Mountain\, and Tell City is her d
 ebut novel. The Netherworlds: Cure of Fates is the first book of a planned 
 series. \n\nThe Netherworlds: Curse of Fates - (Adult Fantasy) The Fates ha
 ve a habit of imprisoning gods too powerful to puppeteer... but now one has
  escaped. Join the gods Loki\, Cupid\, and The Grim Reaper as they find the
  escaped prisoner and use him to overthrow the Fates. \n\nTell City: A Nove
 l - (Young Adult Fantasy) Charles D Garrett's prophetic dream calls him to 
 hitchhike across America to rural Indiana. There he discovers a dark secret
  and is swept up into a battle against gods for the last remaining oracle o
 n Earth.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230914T181255Z
LOCATION:Art Sanctuary\, 190 N Sycamore St\, Martinsville\, IN 46151\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Author’s Reception for New Book Release
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
